## HTTP Error Codes: [link](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_HTTP_status_codes)
 - 200 - OK
 - 400 - Bad Request
 - 500 - Internal Server Error
 - 201 - Created
 - 304 - Not Modified
 - 404 - Not Found
 - 401 - Not Authorized
 - 403 - Forbidden
 - 429 - Too Many Requests
